metadata.name: El Niño Maya
metadata.description:
"El Niño Maya" is a self portrait painting on canvas inspired by my experiences growing up exposed to the extreme poverty found throughout Guatemala City and the contrast of a quiet suburban life found here in the states.  Soy el producto de dos culturas. 

m. 2022 
4000 x 4000 px
𝘓𝘢 𝘌𝘵𝘦𝘳𝘯𝘢 𝘗𝘳𝘪𝘮𝘢𝘷𝘦𝘳𝘢 series 

Based from an original painting by Os
36 x 36 inches
Acrylic, pastel, ink, and oil on canvas
Digitized May 2022
